{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "", "eventName": "", "entryType": "EXTRA", "storyCode": "", "avgTag": "", "storyName": "幕後黑手", "storyInfo": "眾人都在歡慶，\n只有Miss.Christine看到了陰謀的始作俑者。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "由此，故事迎來終結。"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燈光關閉，演員離場，紅幕布緩緩拉上。"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曲終人散，一切又重歸寂靜。"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL_castlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨大的玩偶倒在舞台上，再也沒了聲響。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_130", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Miss.Christine很想用這柔韌的縫布磨磨爪子，或者窩在玩偶爆開的棉花裡小憩一會兒。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但對她來說，現在的首要任務，還是確認傀影的狀態。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從傀影失去心智的那刻起，Miss.Christine就一直在給羅德島的幹員們留下線索。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然，她並不清楚那些愚鈍的傢伙能否理解腳印、爪痕與牙印的含義......"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而就結果來看，Miss.Christine還是十分滿意的。"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "優雅的女士輕聲嘟囔了幾句。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位斐迪亞還在確認玩偶的狀態，女士知道，他在擔心玩偶的操控者會突然現身，將傀影再次置入劇團的陰影。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "答案自然是不會，女士早已洞察。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "探查無果後，斐迪亞前去攙扶傀影。起初，斐迪亞的語氣中帶著一絲似有似無的戒備。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他也曾是劇團的成員，直至今日，他仍畏懼劇團的一切。"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在確認傀影真正回歸後，他也卸下了心頭的重擔，恢復了之前那副輕柔憂鬱的模樣。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他走下舞台，向著古堡的出口而去。"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傀影在階梯頂端駐足沉思，試圖將自己如亂麻一般的心緒整理妥當。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而女士，就在他腳邊舔舐著爪子。"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出於天性，女士不經意地四下張望，在感到脊背上的瘙癢後，又自然地扭過頭去，準備撓撓自己的後背。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但就在轉頭的瞬間，女士停下了動作。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那裡，她看到了......"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL02", "fadetime": 2.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL02", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 0.9, "yScaleTo": 0.9, "duration": 40.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位不速之客。"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 5.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}